# Model checkpoints — often gigabytes, not reconstructable from code alone.
# Git is not designed for large binaries. Store these in cloud storage (S3, GCS)
# or use DVC/Git LFS for tracked large files instead.
# See Lesson 09 (Data Management) for DVC / Git LFS workflows.
*.pt
*.pth
*.safetensors

# Other large ML artefacts (add as needed)
*.onnx
*.bin
*.h5
